object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct transactionhistory.SystemId, transactionhistory.ParentId, transactionhistory.CMMContainer, transactionhistory.Id, transactionhistory.TransactionCd, transactionhistory.TransactionEffectiveDt, transactionhistory.TransactionEffectiveTm, transactionhistory.TransactionUser, transactionhistory.TransactionDt, transactionhistory.TransactionTm, transactionhistory.TransactionLongDescription, transactionhistory.TransactionShortDescription, transactionhistory.TransactionNumber, transactionhistory.SubmissionNumber, transactionhistory.InforcePremiumAmt, transactionhistory.InforceChangePremiumAmt, transactionhistory.WrittenPremiumAmt, transactionhistory.WrittenChangePremiumAmt, transactionhistory.CancelTypeCd, transactionhistory.CancelRequestedByCd, transactionhistory.RewriteToProductVersion, transactionhistory.PremiumCalculationDt, transactionhistory.NewPolicyEffectiveDt, transactionhistory.NewPolicyExpirationDt, transactionhistory.ReleaseHoldReason, transactionhistory.ChangeInfoRef, transactionhistory.BookDt, transactionhistory.MasterTransactionNumber, transactionhistory.ReplacedByTransactionNumber, transactionhistory.ReplacementOfTransactionNumber, transactionhistory.UnAppliedByTransactionNumber, transactionhistory.UnApplyOfTransactionNumber, transactionhistory.StatProcessedInd, transactionhistory.OutputTypeCd, transactionhistory.ApplicationRef, transactionhistory.HoldType, transactionhistory.SourceCd, transactionhistory.DelayInvoiceInd, transactionhistory.PaymentTypeCd, transactionhistory.CheckNumber, transactionhistory.PaymentAmt, transactionhistory.ConversionGroup, transactionhistory.ConversionTemplateIdRef, transactionhistory.ConversionJobRef, transactionhistory.RenewalProviderRef, transactionhistory.RenewalSubProducerCd, transactionhistory.WrittenFeeAmt, transactionhistory.WrittenCommissionFeeAmt, transactionhistory.TransactionCommissionAmt, transactionhistory.FutureTermAutoTransactionInd, transactionhistory.UnapplySource, transactionhistory.ChargeReinstatementFeeInd, transactionhistory.ReferenceNumber, transactionhistory.RowId 
FROM
 transactionhistory  transactionhistory inner join advrxxchangedbeans advrxxchangedbeans
on transactionhistory.Systemid=advrxxchangedbeans.Systemid
and transactionhistory.cmmcontainer=advrxxchangedbeans.cmmcontainer
where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$M_StartDt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$M_EndDt'
